sub_title: International Officer, VVD l Global Policy Fellow, ITS Rio | EU, Tech, Digital, Western Balkans, Caucasus
summary: As a former-think-tanker-turned-civil-servant-turned-political-international-officer, I have experience in EU digital policy and international affairs from a broad perspective. Having worked both in Brussels and the Hague, I strive to be a bridge between Europe and the Netherlands. In my current position I am particularly focused on building bridges between the liberal community in Eastern Europe and the liberal VVD party in the Netherlands. I am passionate about Europe, foreign policy & diplomacy, mobility, and the emerging policy fields of cyber, digital & technology.
